            Summary = "Power-user and admin edge cases for the AI Assistant: temperature/maxContextChunks tuning, built-in vs custom assistants and deletion rules, capability gating and container-down degradation, RAG document indexing, and the Help panel's cross-tab sync and 50-message cap.",
